|a|=|b|=|c|= 1
\left|\frac{a-b}{1-a\overline{b}}\right| = 1
|ab+bc+ca| = |a+b+c|
|x|=1
\bar x=1/x\ 
1=|x|^2=x\bar x
|a-b|=|a|\cdot |1- a/b|=1\cdot |1-a\bar b|
|ab+bc+ca|=\left|\frac{ab+bc+ca}{abc}\right|=|\bar c+\bar a+\bar b|=|a+b+c|. 
|b|=1,|1-a\bar b|=\frac{|b||1-a\bar b|}{| b|}=|b(1-a\bar b)|=|b-ab^2|=|b-a|=|a-b|
a=e^{i\alpha}=cis\alpha,b=cis\beta,c=cis\gamma 
|1-a\bar b|=|1-e^{i\alpha}e^{-i\beta}|=|1-e^{i(\alpha-\beta)}|=|1-\cos(\alpha-\beta)-i\sin(\alpha-\beta)|=\sqrt{(1-\cos(\alpha-\beta))^2+(-\sin(\alpha-\beta))^2}=\sqrt{2-2\cos(\alpha-\beta)}
|ab+bc+ca|=|abc(a^{-1}+b^{-1}+c^{-1})|=|abc||a^{-1}+b^{-1}+c^{-1}|=|\bar a+\bar b+\bar c|
|abc|=|a||b||c|=1
|ab+bc+ca|=|\bar a+\bar b+\bar c|=|\overline{a+b+c}|=|a+b+c|
